Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:03.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:07.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make \Nsure to keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:09.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.84,0:00:21.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Ouchy, ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:23.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.63,0:00:25.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:26.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:27.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please lemme off!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:30.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who said he wanted to ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:55.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right! I'll yell it out countless times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.63,0:01:00.70,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe your every tomorrow will be shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:03.05,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The intersection of all people
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.05,0:01:05.66,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,whose dreams have come true is one point:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.66,0:01:10.29,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Never giving up.  And that's why we're not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:15.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,When it seems like you'll be blown away by the headwinds,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:17.62,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,grasp this hand, try to take a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:20.89,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're not alone anymore, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:26.00,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Go forward, more and more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:28.52,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up on your awesome dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:29.78,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.78,0:01:31.25,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Move on, my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:33.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, with the light shining down upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:35.71,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think about something like giving up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.71,0:01:38.14,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you trade being hurt again for strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:43.63,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes, always looking straight ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:47.91,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,can surely see the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:15.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Akane Resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:19.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the most popular tourist spot in the Kingdom, located by the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:25.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a giant amusement park and a five-star hotel next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.70,0:02:29.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a beach which will keep you coming back again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:35.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's the sea expanding out to the infinite horizon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:38.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the tickets they received from Loke,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:44.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu and the others are visiting and having some excellent time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:46.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back my boxers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:48.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not on your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:51.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, "Don't use Happy to cover yourself up!" {That construction requires quotes. If you had said, "I'm telling you not to use Happy to cover yourself up," you wouldn't need the quotes.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:53.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama... So bold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:58.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tower of Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:15.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But today sure was fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:18.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:14.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:17.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no such thing as freedom in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:35.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:41.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When did I fall asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:13.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I really do feel more at ease while I'm in armor. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:17.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no help for a woman like me... 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:20.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:22.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go have some fun downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:24.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu and Gray are already down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:26.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They wanted to go win some games!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:28.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes! They have a place like that, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:44.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look the part?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:47.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, maybe that's a little {\i1}too{\i0} flashy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:48.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:57.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes taking a day to pamper myself... isn't such a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:17.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,17! Come on, 17!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, 17!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:25.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's 17!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kiddin' me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:30.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,17!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:32.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, please refrain from...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:35.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it stopped on 17 once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:36.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.55,0:06:38.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,17!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:39.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crying isn't going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:42.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to 17!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:45.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, they're so immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:46.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:52.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:54.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that Phantom woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:56.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,17! Come back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:58.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, please stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:05.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Casinos are places for grownups... For dandies! Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:12.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:15.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only two paths that men can travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.29,0:07:16.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.87,0:07:21.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:23.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Live on as a dandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:30.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or stop and meet your end. Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:34.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Phantom was disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:39.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Juvia is now a Free Wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:44.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I take it you want to join Fairy Tail, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:46.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Juvia does!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.31,0:07:49.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But after all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:52.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't mind, but I'm not sure what the master would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:54.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia will do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:57.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say that so lightly if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:07:59.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray Fullbuster?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:09.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:12.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the parade has started outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:13.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:14.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:16.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:18.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:19.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:21.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:23.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:25.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:28.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:29.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:31.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really on a roll today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:35.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dealer change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:36.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:41.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling that I won't lose no matter who I'm up against.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:42.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:47.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... why don't we play a special game?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:56.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play a game where your life's on the line, Erza-neesan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:00.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... Sho?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:02.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sho, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:04.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been quite a while, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were... safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:10.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:13.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:15.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:20.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'll tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:27.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow you to lay a finger on Gray-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:29.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia will be your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:34.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Danger is closing in around Erza-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:40.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You found her already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:43.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can clean up here? Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it went dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:50.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Dark Lineage Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:53.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:57.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? I can't see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:59.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:01.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here! But... where's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:04.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:08.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A gunshot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:11.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:14.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sho!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:15.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:17.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:27.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:29.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The people are in the cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:30.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:31.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Intrigued?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:37.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I can use it now too, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:38.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You... What have you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:43.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:46.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Feelin' chip an' dipper?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:50.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Milliana... You can use magic too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:52.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it been, Er-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:55.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let Lucy go! She's my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:57.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:00.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were your friends too once... Isn't that right, Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:02.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were friends...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:06.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:10.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is... until you betrayed us, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:16.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't abuse Erza so much, Sho.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:21.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who's a dandy should keep his emotions in check.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:23.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a blockhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:24.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:27.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You grew a pretty hot body there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:30.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... Wally?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:32.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it's not surprising you wouldn't recognize me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:36.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, when I was called "Mad Dog Wally,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:39.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a lot more... rough around the edges.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.19,0:11:44.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You also use magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:45.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:49.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you get the hang of it, anyone can use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:51.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:52.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:56.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:58.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are they calling you their sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:03.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not actually their sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:05.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all together in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:11.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But haven't you been in Fairy Tail since you were really young?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:13.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:17.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:18.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:20.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To take you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:23.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Release Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:28.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we go home, Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:31.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you do what we say...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:37.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.27,0:12:41.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:43.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:56.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've recovered our objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:57.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:58.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:00.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I used a tranquilizer shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:03.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you taking Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:11.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you guys were up against Natsu or Gray they'd blow you away real quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:15.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but they're the ones that got blown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:17.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They were overrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:20.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:22.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:24.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:36.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In another five minutes your body'll be completely bent backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.97,0:13:40.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, Milliana, I have a present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:44.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a kitty-cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:46.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:47.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:49.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Milliana, bind Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:53.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A kitty-cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:53.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Milliana, we're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:57.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:02.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming back... to the Tower of Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:06.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just know that Jellal will be pleased!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:11.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tower of Heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:14.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-They finished it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:23.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:29.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh, I'm gonna bust outta this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:32.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:37.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Giant Crab, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:38.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:46.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:47.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cancer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:50.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then, Taurus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:51.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Loke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:15:00.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use magic... Is it because of this rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:04.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:06.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, was that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:12.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, see, since I can't get out, I was trying to prick it with this paper knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:16.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:17.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We might be able to get free!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:21.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The knife from inside the card poked me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:21.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Close-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:28.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I don't know why, but that means that stuff from inside the card can affect the outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:29.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:33.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then does my knife look like it's sticking out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:34.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's still flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:39.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I felt pain, then its force can be felt outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:43.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Trying cutting my rope with that knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:45.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:50.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:52.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't rush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:54.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, just get on with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:57.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, they're cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:00.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! You saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:02.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:04.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, it's your turn to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:07.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'll come back and save you, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:08.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:13.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, Gray... They're fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:19.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:24.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:32.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-It'll be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fix you up, promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:37.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:43.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, one of the Element 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:45.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:48.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not our enemy anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:50.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:53.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama was inside of Juvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:55.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:58.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not inside of you... Inside of Juvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:00.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:06.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After it got dark all of a sudden, I figured I'd leave a double and see how things turned out, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:12.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for him not to be discovered by the enemy, Juvia protected Gray-sama in her Water Lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:16.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And thanks to your meddling, he got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:19.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, where's Natsu and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:23.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about Natsu, but Happy and Erza have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:28.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:30.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:31.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:34.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:37.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it normal to go shooting people in the mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.65,0:17:38.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:40.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy could get hurt really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:44.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, normal people would be totally KOed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Such is the Salamander.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:48.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn blockhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:50.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:51.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:53.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:57.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a nose on him that'd put animals to shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:04.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blockhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:48.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Jellal, I'm here to report that they've captured Erza and are heading here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:52.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:54.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you let that traitor live until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:59.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With your magical power, you should have been able to dispose of her easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:04.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that wouldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The world would be too boring a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:14.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, now that the Tower of Heaven is complete, allowing her to live would cause issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:24.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will become a living sacrifice to our aspiration, Erza Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.79,0:19:42.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:46.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside a ship, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:47.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:53.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Inside a ship heading toward the Tower of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:59.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.25,0:20:01.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you untie me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:03.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't plan to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:05.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:07.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're a traitor, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:14.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless. Milliana's tubes have the power of sealing magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:17.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do anything about them on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how powerful you are, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:23.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.09,0:20:28.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then would you at least allow me to requip into armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:33.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid... to return to that tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:40.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I'm wearing armor... the fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:44.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you look good in that dress, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:55.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:57.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sho...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:02.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed you! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:06.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:11.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:14.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...betray Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:21.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:31.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, over here, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:33.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sho, don't be so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:36.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're even louder, Wally!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.32,0:21:38.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Milliana.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.10,0:21:42.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, if we don't hurry, they'll find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:44.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:48.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if they find out... 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:55.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know... What they do to the kids that are found out...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.48,0:21:58.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, there's nothing to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.78,0:22:01.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:06.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to get our freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:09.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our future, and our aspirations.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:17.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.46,0:22:19.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.15,0:24:00.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Happy's been kidnapped, this time I'm doin' the preview all by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.28,0:24:04.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, calling to order the first "Plan to Save Happy and Erza" meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.37,0:24:05.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The plan is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.77,0:24:08.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Barge in through the front door and blow away the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.73,0:24:11.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The codename is "CHARGE!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.25,0:24:13.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.02,0:24:16.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Jellal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.47,0:24:18.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Happy... Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.18,0:24:21.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand when you're older.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.46,0:24:23.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That doesn't make any sense.
